songs.title: Asher Roth Freestyle - 2009 XXL Freshman
songs.lyrics:
Yo
I did yoga right when I woke up
Yoghurt, fresh fruit and granola
Soy milk, diet soda
Don’t drink it no more, it’s bad for ya
Yo I’m Soda-delighted!
‘Cause I’m such a-a white kid!
I like it, it’s cool
Where’s the mic at? Let’s duel
Nah, not yet
Let’s put Soulja Boy on and watch the white kids “Youuuu!”
Go school! Yay books!
I like chess, I’ll take your rook
I like breasts, I’ll take a look
Won’t say nothing ‘till you befriend you on Facebook

Come on, guys! Come on, guys
How ‘bout some love?
